WEBVTT

1
00:00:17.390 --> 00:00:18.969
She signed the papers.

2
00:00:18.969 --> 00:00:19.809
What did she want?

3
00:00:19.809 --> 00:00:20.940
Mark.

4
00:00:20.940 --> 00:00:21.780
And the apartment.

5
00:00:21.780 --> 00:00:24.239
Well, at least we know she's not a gold digger.

6
00:00:24.239 --> 00:00:26.679
Still, she was my wife.

7
00:00:26.679 --> 00:00:45.369
Why are a hundred million affair divorces concluded?

8
00:00:45.369 --> 00:00:50.960
You can't come in here without your parents.

9
00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.719
I can lead you, you know.

10
00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:54.840
And that is not the thing.

11
00:00:54.840 --> 00:00:56.000
What do you know?

12
00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:04.239
You don't even have a dad.

13
00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:05.840
Watch it, boy.

14
00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:09.280
Somebody's got to teach you how to behave.

15
00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:10.120
Stop.

